:: Choice12 [Choice12] {"position":"600,600","size":"100,100"}
 <div class="Nochoice">
Regardless, any of your answers have no meaning now. This is the end, there is nothing for you to go back for. Nothing to fear or cry. Now come, follow me and I will take you where you need to be.
  </div>
  
   <span class="Followbutton">
    (link-goto: "Follow", "Followpath")
  </span>


:: College [Firstdorm] {"position":"850,725","size":"100,100"}
<div class="urvoice">
Within a blink of an eye, you appear in a messy college dorm. The walls was nearly covered with assignments, prints and sticky notes, the bed's sheet was uneven, and its lovely pillow, on the hard, wooden floor. The desk contain a open laptop, with some folders and notebooks, open and spread against the desk. You observed the room once more, you spot:

 </div>
 
 <div class="Collegechoicesbuttons">

  <span class="college1button">
    (link-goto: "A Manuscript paper", "Manuscriptpaper")
  </span>
  
  <span class="college2button">
    (link-goto: "A photo frame" , "Photoframe")
  </span>
  
    <span class="college3button">
    (link-goto: "A dorm door" , "ExitDoor")
  </span>
  
  </div>
  
</div>



