:: ExitDoor {"position":"950,850","size":"100,100"}



:: First [Hospital] {"position":"600,350","size":"100,100"}
<div class="textBubble">
<span style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold;">
Random doctors and nurses:
</span>

  "Note, date and time of death."
  
  "March 11, 2024. Time 5:39pm."</p>   <!-- This whole text is HTML, the </p> is a bulit in space -->
 </div>
 
 <div class="SelfBubble">
 Those words were the last thing you heard before you stop hearing at all. 
  </div>
  
  <span class="next-button">
    (link-goto: "NEXT", "Nexthospital")
  </span>
  


:: Followpath [Continue] {"position":"600,725","size":"100,100"}
<div class="Followchat">
You start to walk, well, more like dragging your feet. Every step feels like a strong force is pushing you backward, aiming to keep you where you are, instead of following.
 </div>

 <div class="Followchat">
You can't help but feel as if something is out of place. You lift your chin, wondering who this person you're speaking to, but you came face with nothing but an eerie, pit-black space, with only a few breeze creeping wiping your sweat. As you open your mouth to speak, a sudden sound, no, a music note, faintly brushes against your ear.
 </div>
 
    <span class="Leavebutton">
    (link-goto: "Stop", "Leavespace")
  </span>


:: Leavespace [Leavespace] {"position":"725,725","size":"100,100"}
<div class="StoppingADippingchat">
You stop dead in your track, turning behind to meet nothing. However, you keep hearing  the music, softly echoing, yearning for a piece of your attention.
 </div>
 
 
 <div class="Voicechat">
Don't go, if you do. You will never want to leave.
 </div>
 
 <div class="StoppingADippingchat">
You continue to stare at the direction of the sound. With enough thought and gut, you rip away from pathway of the voice, jogging towards it.
 </div>
 
 
    <span class="gocollegebutton">
    (link-goto: "Jog", "College")
  </span>


:: Manuscriptpaper {"position":"700,850","size":"100,100"}



:: Nexthospital [Nexthospital] {"position":"600,475","size":"100,100"}
 <div class="dialogue">
Do you remember your name? Do you even remember what you last ate? 
  </div>

<div class="button-row">

  <span class="Choice1button">
    (link-goto: '"No."', "Choice12")
  </span>
  
  <span class="Choice2button">
    (link-goto: ' "Where am I?" ', "Choice12")
  </span>
  
  </div>
  
</div>



